short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Experience an edgy blend of futuristic AI and eerie skull imagery in this bold live wallpaper for Chrome. 💀🤖⚙️

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Transform your browser into a cybernetic dystopia with this Skull AI live wallpaper. Perfect for fans of dark aesthetics, sci-fi, and tech-inspired art, this wallpaper features a high-tech skull glowing with neon lights, hinting at the merging of AI and humanity. Each new tab opens to a bold, futuristic vibe that is both haunting and captivating, ideal for those who enjoy a bit of mystery and edge in their digital space.

Key Features
🖼️ Live Skull AI Wallpaper: A detailed, glowing skull with AI-inspired neon effects in an intense design.
🔗 Customizable Site Shortcuts: Add shortcuts to your favorite sites for quick access.
🔍 Google Search Bar: Seamless search bar that keeps the sleek, high-tech vibe.
🕒 Clock & Date Display: Minimalist clock and date for futuristic functionality.
🔗 Quick Access Links: “Remove Extension” and “More Extensions” links in the lower left corner for easy management.
This extension is perfect for tech enthusiasts, sci-fi fans, and anyone who loves a touch of the dark digital aesthetic with a modern twist. Add intrigue to your new tabs with this Skull AI live wallpaper!
